title: The Art of Star Wars (1979) -Titleman- PDF [Slender]
description:
Publisher: Ballantine Books (February 1982)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 0345306279
ISBN-13: 978-0345306272

This is the first in a series of art books, and is designed as a companion volume to the film "Star Wars". It contains the complete movie script by George Lucas, and - through sketches, paintings and photographs - aims to recreate the imaginative process that went into the making of the film.
